'''Daniel Naprous''' is an actor and stunt performer.

He appeared in the [[Season 4|fourth season]] of ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]'' as [[Oznak zo Pahl]], a champion for[[ Meereen]]. He appeared in the episode "[[Breaker of Chains]]".

He has also appeared in other episodes of Game of Thrones as a stunt performer.
